{"tid":17797,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"200年觀音古廟 不設防遭賊仔爆竊","createTime":"2016-12-02T03:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T03:27:59.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34354966da4db5022e7e104781a5adb5ed3192d8","tid":17797,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161201/large/1480560201_708c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161201%2Flarge%2F1480560201_708c.jpg&h=3fed5d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上水蕉徑龍潭觀音古廟，今早7時23分，49歲姓賴負責人返回廟宇時，發現兩個木製香油箱被人撬開，警員接報到場調查，損失數百元。<br />\n姓賴負責人稱，為方便善信參拜，古廟最近24小時開放，今早返回廟宇時，發現兩個木製香油箱被人撬開，估計損失300-500元。他表示，年半前試過被賊人撬窗入內爆竊，當時未全日開放，今次事件後會加強保安，安裝閉路電視，並取消通宵開放。<br />\n觀音古廟有超過200年歷史，前身是糧倉，其後獲政府批出改建為廟宇供奉觀音，廟內有一個鐵製香油箱，兩日前已經清空，另有3個木製香油箱，捐獻較小，今次賊人撬開其中2個木製的香油箱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161201/55988776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161201%2F55988776&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAKEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=3e80622c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161201%2F55988776&h=4d609e8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161201/55988776</a>"},{"pid":"5f299d6d0693546356dad0852b3837f1f80d5876","tid":17797,"uid":28394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:27:59.000Z","msg":"特別方法借庫"}]}